# 899 stacks of 10-12 shows covering the whole Fugazi repertoire (94 songs), one for each show in the Fugazi Live Series.

899 stacks of 10-12 shows covering the whole Fugazi repertoire (94
songs), one for each show in the Fugazi Live Series.

## Usage

``` r
gid_initial_gid_sound_quality
```

## Format

dataframe with one row for each combination of initial show and stacked
show.

- gid_initial:

  show id of the initial show, used to identify each stack of shows

- gid:

  show id of each show contained within each stack

- sound_quality:

  Sound quality rating: Excellent, Very Good, Good, or Poor.

## Source

https://www.dischord.com/fugazi_live_series
